I haven't checked if all the mp3's are complete. They also don't seem to come from the same source of recording/ripping. However, all the other copies out there seem to be clones and have the same ordering mistake. I hope this clears up some confusion.

Tom78 - I can tell from your comment to CaptOmerta that you clearly only get your news from official / mainstream sources. But you have to remember these two very good quotes from Orwell.

"Early in life I had noticed that no event is ever correctly reported in a newspaper." (I feel this is also true with televised news).

"Political language... is designed to make lies sound truthful and murder respectable, and to give an appearance of solidity to pure wind."

Of course, this is only opinion and we all know one shouldn't make fact out of opinion, but I feel that it is true. . .and I'm sure millions of other people throughout the world feel this opinion is true also.

And who better to say it than someone who worked at the BBC??

And you can clearly see how much the mainstream media lie about the world we're living in by simply Googling "30,000 scientists" and think about how much the media call the UN IPCC "the worlds top 2,500 scientists".
Recommended reading as we are approaching the fiction irl.
